description: Datalox pack rules for Cursor. Detect skills, use linked pattern docs, patch reusable knowledge, and keep control artifacts current.
globs:
  - "skills/**/SKILL.md"
  - ".datalox/**/*.md"
  - "DATALOX.md"
  - "AGENTS.md"
